nday-cable-originals-6-8-2015.html|title=Top 100 Monday Cable Originals: August 6, 2015|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=June 9, 2015|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|accessdate=June 9, 2015}}</ref>\n| March 28, 2016\n|0.77<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-monday-cable-originals-network-finals-3-28-2016.html|title=UPDATED: SHOWBUZZDAILY's Top 150 Monday Cable Originals & Network Finals: March 28, 2016|work=showbuzzdaily.com}}</ref> \n| [[2015\u201316 United States network television schedule|2015\u201316]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | 1.00<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/the-fosters-season-three-ratings-37077/|title=The Fosters: Season Three Ratings|work=TV Series Finale|date=March 30, 2016|accessdate=September 2, 2016}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#f9f9f9;\"\n! style=\"background:#F9F9F9;text-align:center\" |  [[List of The Fosters episodes#Season 4: 2016|4]]\n| 20\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <small>Mondays 8:00&nbsp;pm (2016)<br>Tuesdays 8:00pm (2017)</small>\n| June 20, 2016\n|0.91<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/06/21/monday-cable-ratings-june-20-2016/|title=Monday cable ratings: \u2018Love & Hip Hop\u2019 returns on top|last=Welch|first=Alex|date=June 21, 2016|accessdate=June 21, 2016|publisher=TVbytheNumbers}}</ref>\n| April 11, 2017\n| 0.72<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-tuesday-cable-originals-network-finals-4-11-2017.html|title=Updated: ShowBuzzDaily's Top 150 Tuesday Cable Originals & Network Finals: November 4, 2017|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|accessdate=April 12, 2017|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=April 12, 2017}}</ref>\n| [[2016\u201317 United States network television schedule|2016\u201317]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{TableTBA}}\n|- style=\"background:#f9f9f9;\"\n! style=\"background:#F9F9F9;text-align:center\" |  [[List of The Fosters episodes#Season 5: 2017|5]]\n| 22\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | Tuesdays 8:00pm